Hello, 
  This is a notification from Find-A-Friend about a study session that has been created or updated.

<% if @post.allow_onid %>
  <%= @post.onid %> would like to request that you come study. You can view this study group at <%= link_to "Oregon State University Find-a-Friend", post_path(@post) %>.
  You can reply to this person using their onid:
  <%= @post.onid %>@onid.oregonstate.edu
<% end %>

Study Event Name:
<%= @post.title %>

Description:
<%= @post.description %>

Location:
<%= @post.location %> 

<% if @post.meeting_time && @post.end_time %>
  From <%= @post.meeting_time.strftime(I18n.t('time.formats.default')) %> to <%= @post.end_time.strftime(I18n.t('time.formats.default')) %>.
<% elsif @post.meeting_time && !@post.end_time %>
  Starting at: <%= @post.meeting_time.strftime(I18n.t('time.formats.default')) %>
<% else %>
  A time has not yet been set for this group meeting.
<% end %>

Sincerely,
  Find-A-Friend
